1
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,730
Hand over the Third Prince.

2
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,720
Anyone who disobeys

3
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:14,800
will be killed on the spot.

4
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:17,080
Young Master Bai, hand over Bai Chuyi as well.

5
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,360
You can't protect her.

6
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,520
Chuyi has already been taken away by Wuyue.

7
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,600
You won't find her.

8
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,480
Stop talking nonsense. Attack!

9
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,720
Huanghuacai!

10
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,960
As long as I'm here, who dares to make a move?

11
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:41,240
Miss Song, you're actually still alive.

12
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,600
What luck.

13
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,160
Song Xuan, you're just in time.

14
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:47,200
Saves me the trouble of finding you.

15
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,680
Sang Biao, kill her.

16
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,240
Huanghuacai!

17
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,530
Huanghuacai, are you alright?

18
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,200
Don't worry. I won't die.

19
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:41,280
It turns out everything was destined.

20
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:44,000
In the end, I still...

21
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,760
couldn't change anything.

22
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,600
Kill! Kill them all!

23
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,280
Stop!

24
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,080
Heir Yuan.

25
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:02,600
Bai Manchuan, I'm not here to save you.

26
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:03,960
The reason I'm here

27
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,120
is solely for the sake of our country and justice.

28
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,600
I'll settle the score with you later.

29
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:13,560
I am late to the rescue.

30
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,080
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

31
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,920
Rise.

32
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,880
Huai, why are you here?

33
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,320
Song Xuan told me.

34
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:23,120
General Song, what do you need from me?

35
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,120
You have a private army, my Lord.

36
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,960
So what if I do?

37
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:30,079
That was bestowed upon the Prince Duan Manor by the Emperor.

38
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:32,280
Then your chance to earn merit has come.

39
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,160
What do you mean?

40
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:36,960
Please keep a close watch on the Marquis Manor these few days.

41
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,960
Once you spot the Bai family and the Third Prince

42
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,560
leaving the manor together,

43
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:44,140
please take your private army to the southern suburbs forest.

44
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:46,680
Why would the Third Prince come to the Marquis Manor?

45
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,740
Someone wants to frame His Highness.

46
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,880
As soon as I saw

47
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:52,079
that Shen Lingbo and Tuoya were outside the Marquis Manor,

48
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,600
and you just happened to come out the side door,

49
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,600
I immediately brought my troops over.

50
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,530
Huai, thank you for your hard work.

51
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,090
So late at night,

52
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,040
how dare you offend the Third Prince here?

53
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,120
What exactly are you trying to do?

54
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,360
Arrest them all!

55
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,160
I lost.

56
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,580
Uncle Zhao!

57
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,700
Uncle Zhao!

58
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,080
Young Master.

59
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,520
We didn't bring shame to the Marquis Manor.

60
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:31,880
No.

61
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:41,320
We won.

62
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,480
Young Master,

63
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,440
Second Miss Shen is locked in the backyard.

64
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,370
She says she wants to see you alone.

65
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,650
What do you want to say to me?

66
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:28,040
The night I arrived in the capital, I was sold to Baihua Tower.

67
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,840
You saved me.

68
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,080
But I ran away.

69
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,440
After that, I found the Prime Minister's Manor,

70
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:39,080
but I was kicked out.

71
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:44,159
Just when I thought I would freeze to death outside,

72
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,810
you walked over.

73
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,560
You shielded me from the wind

74
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,060
and reached out your hand.

75
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,770
The way you looked at me,

76
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,060
I'll never forget it as long as I live.

77
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:04,240
Back then, I thought I was special to you.

78
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,600
But later I realized,

79
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,920
you treat everyone the same.

80
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:13,260
So I wanted to become your exception.

81
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,360
No matter the cost.

82
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,490
But just when I thought I was about to succeed,

83
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,920
Song Xuan appeared.

84
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,250
I was jealous of her.

85
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,700
And I hated how easily she could have you.

86
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:30,610
But I could only tell myself over and over,

87
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,480
"It's okay. I can do this."

88
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,200
But later,

89
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,520
I saw that your eyes held only Song Xuan.

90
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,680
I wanted power.

91
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,280
Because only by standing at the top

92
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:52,159
would I be worthy of standing by your side.

93
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,330
I've done so many wrong things.

94
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,940
And harmed so many people.

95
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,560
At the end of this road,

96
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,010
lies the abyss of no return.

97
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09,880
Manchuan, will you look at me properly one last time?

98
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,360
Since that is the case...

99
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:45,040
If there is a next life...

100
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,480
Forget it.

101
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,080
Actually,

102
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,440
let's not have a next life.

103
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:01,880
Lingbo.

104
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:23,250
You've been waiting here alone for a long time, haven't you?

105
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,480
Not that long.

106
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:28,760
Zhaohua, we've been through so much together.

107
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:31,960
There's something I've always wanted to tell you.

108
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:32,760
Don't say it.

109
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,960
Can you promise me one thing first?

110
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,640
I want to enter the Palace and become a female official.

111
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,570
What did you say?

112
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:44,159
My sister-in-law was so amazing back then.

113
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:46,080
I want to be like her too.

114
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:49,120
I can't fight enemies on the battlefield,

115
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,760
but you must let me serve my country.

116
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,600
Oh, little Chuyi.

117
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,440
Can't you spend more time with your father?

118
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:03,160
Father, I have more important things to do.

119
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,920
Do you really have to go now?

120
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,800
I belong to the grasslands, after all.

121
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:09,200
Besides, Aunt Wu Yue said

122
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,880
that as long as I return,

123
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:13,920
Da Sheng and the Yueshi Kingdom can have true peace.

124
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:16,680
Chuyi, my sister.

125
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:18,600
Why are you leaving?

126
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:23,000
Chuyi, please don't go.

127
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,080
If your mother were here,

128
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,940
she would surely tell you,

129
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:29,360
"Bring more clothes. It's cold there."

130
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,200
Chuyi, remember this.

131
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,520
The Marquis Zhongyi Manor will always be your home.

132
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,180
We will always be your family.

133
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:40,080
I want to go with you too.

134
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,160
What for?

135
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,960
You're afraid to even get near a horse.

136
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,280
I can practice!

137
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:47,680
Adai, you should stay and keep me company.

138
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,080
I'm leaving then.

139
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,120
Remember to write.

140
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,600
I will. Of course I will.

141
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,320
I'll write whenever I miss you.

142
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:06,760
Let's go.

143
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,240
Let's go.

144
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,440
Chuyi!

145
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,280
Chuyi!

146
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:13,720
Chuyi!

147
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,820
Wait for my return!

148
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,160
Young Master, do you yield?

149
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:01,960
I yield.

150
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,080
To whom?

151
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,200
To you.

152
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:05,760
In what way?

153
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,240
In every way.
